# Dependencies
node_modules/
# ...also as a symlink (worktrees symlink node_modules → main checkout); the
# trailing-slash pattern above only matches a real directory, so a bare
# `node_modules` symlink would otherwise be stage-able (a past accident).
node_modules
apps/*/node_modules

